{"tid":801073,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]等黎sir我教動物台手足襯衫脫毒","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:38:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T03:20:01.000Z","uid":8307,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c26a6f7fe737bbfbcec8fbb44d624d2b567a7f7e","tid":801073,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:38:35.000Z","msg":"相信動物台手足都想比啲好印象比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔cow女,著衫見工都可以加下分咁<br />\n正所謂人靠衣裝,就算生得樣衰,打扮得好睇都起碼加返70分<br />\n如果金城武個樣係100分著咩都咁型<br />\n你個樣係零分都好,都可以靠著衫拎到70分<br />\n加埋啲行為講野技巧上100分都唔係發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望各位手足都可以好似我黎sir咁早日脫毒<br />\n特登開呢個post教下大家襯衫<br />\n<br />\n先貼一個英倫復古風格:<br />\n裝飾:<br />\n<img src=\"https://alexnld.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3bd9601d-8787-47ce-a18a-c4398cfe86a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Falexnld.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F3bd9601d-8787-47ce-a18a-c4398cfe86a9.jpg&h=f727e42b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/183643_e28d700405a60a7c0ec36db407a2cc88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F183643_e28d700405a60a7c0ec36db407a2cc88.jpg&h=17261505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上身:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/183709_eb1708fdaa68adeb42d160e09f7f355f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F183709_eb1708fdaa68adeb42d160e09f7f355f.jpg&h=692bc090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中間加件恤衫/T-shirt都ok<br />\n<br />\n下身:<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/183751_606ed29dc5092eeb041eff9548fba009.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F183751_606ed29dc5092eeb041eff9548fba009.jpg&h=4bd7b7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加多對皮鞋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/183821_0e4c492cc9d5236185715ac3941b43f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F183821_0e4c492cc9d5236185715ac3941b43f7.jpg&h=3af0fe2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fbd1a51f15977f31fa90cb89074d3d0813886e","tid":801073,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"af952b9a7b019b2abba0d71971b7e77d31c2ab4f","tid":801073,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8fbd1a51f15977f31fa90cb89074d3d0813886e","tid":801073,"uid":6527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:41:10.000Z","msg":"55"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:41:58.000Z","msg":"hi雪菜b"},{"pid":"e5c44ad8cfc6eafa5561df10b6f0cf9b0a4d32a4","tid":801073,"uid":21286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:42:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebbf6d4ad0c1f2d9148ba2fa6eaf4abcad25fcf8","tid":801073,"uid":99733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:42:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52356777953f65563a38f604e4023a434bbc2a8a","tid":801073,"uid":5077,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:42:42.000Z","msg":"啱啱咁著一落街就有女警搭訕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4501aefa47258e0baebdb3f7bec084f91108203f","tid":801073,"uid":147871,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.reactiongifs.com/r/2013/10/tim-and-eric-mind-blown.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reactiongifs.com%2Fr%2F2013%2F10%2Ftim-and-eric-mind-blown.gif&h=67a3cb1d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"